view.welcome: ʻOku talitali lelei koe ki he ARC!  Faʻu ha ngaahi vitio fakatautaha mo ha taha ʻo ʻetau holograms pea fokotuʻu ia ki hoʻo ngaahi senolo mitia fakasosiale!
view.text-step-1: Fili ha hologram mei he laipeli.
view.text-step-2: Ko fakalahi moʻoni ʻeni, ko ia scan ʻa e feituʻu ʻoku ʻataa mo hoʻo meʻa faitaa mei he tafaʻaki ki he tafaʻaki ʻi ha sekoni ʻe 3-5 ʻa ia ʻoku ke fie maʻu ke ʻi ai ʻa e ngaue hologram.
view.text-step-3-part-1: Lomiʻi tuʻo taha ʻi he screen ʻi he feituʻu ʻoku ke fie maʻu ai ʻa e hologram.
view.text-step-3-part-2: TOKONI!  Lomiʻi ʻi ha feituʻu kehe ke ʻunuakiʻi ʻa e hologram ki ha tuʻunga ʻe taha.
view.text-step-3-part-3: TOKONI!  Te ke lava ʻo resize ʻa e hologram ʻaki haʻo vakuʻi laʻusi pe fakalahi ʻa e screen ʻaki ho motuʻa tuhu mo e foʻi tuhu fakahokohoko fakamotuʻalea.
view.text-step-4-part-1: Lomiʻi tuʻo ua ʻi he lekooti kulokula ke KAMATA hoʻo hiki vitioo.
view.text-step-4-part-2: Lomiʻi tuʻo ua ʻa e meʻa lomi lekooti kulokula ke TAʻOFI.
